<% content_for :subject, "❌ Reservation Declined: #{@property.name}" %>

<h2><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Reservation Declined</h2>
<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
<p>Unfortunately, your reservation for <strong><%= @property.name %></strong> from <%= @reservation.start_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> to <%= @reservation.end_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> has been declined.</p>

<p>You may explore other available properties on SCBooker.</p>
